PigeonHoleGenerator - Class in ProblemGenerators
Created by ohlbach on 09.09.2018.
This class is for generating variations of pigeonhole problems of arbitrary size.
There are n holes and m pigeons
Each pigeon must be placed into exactly one hole.
PigeonHoleGenerator(int, int, Object[]) - Constructor for class ProblemGenerators.PigeonHoleGenerator
creates the generator.
pigeons - Variable in class ProblemGenerators.PigeonHoleGenerator
the number of pigeons
